{{BLP sources|date=May 2010}}

'''Vahid Evazzadeh'''  [ <U+0648><U+062D><U+06CC><U+062F> <U+0639><U+0648><U+0636><U+200C><U+0632><U+0627><U+062F><U+0647> ] is an award-winning<ref>Politiken [Danish newspaper] Thursday 7th March, 2002</ref> [[Iran]]ian [[filmmaker]] and [[theatre director]]. He lives in [[Denmark]]<ref>Marstal, Henrik, Danmark if<U+00F8>lge Vahid , ''Borger i smilets land'', Benny Andersen og danskheden, Gyldendal Publishing House 2005</ref> since 2001.

